The GoogleSheets plugin lets you import from [[Google Sheets|https://www.google.com/sheets/about/]] into TiddlyWiki.

*Each Google sheet row becomes a tiddler.
*The first row - the "column heads" - define the tiddler fields.

;Note
*Imported tiddlers appear in the //Recent// sidebar and are listed in the Import list.
*@@color:red; Importing overwrites@@ existing tiddlers having the same title.


